Class ItemMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • ItemMenu

  • public class ItemMenu
extends java.lang.Object
    Item Menu is the class to contain the items in Menu. There are three list that contain the information of all the items in menu. When ordering the items, customer would choose from this list. This class has functions to add, remove or store the items.
